      "README.md": "# __ATM_TITLE__\n\n__ATM_DESC__\n\n## What this does\nActive Directory enumeration & abuse detection: ldap3 user/group enumeration, kerberoastable account discovery (SPNs), AS-REP-roastable accounts (no preauth), domain trust enumeration, GPO ACL inspection, LLMNR/NBT-NS poisoning fingerprint.\n\n## Install\n```bash\npip install -r requirements.txt\n```\n\n## Usage\n```bash\npython3 cli.py scan --target ldap://dc.corp.local --output reports/ad.json\n```\n\n## Requirements\nldap3>=2.9\nimpacket>=0.12\n\n\n## Output\n`reports/scan.json` — raw findings.\nRun `python3 cli.py report --input reports/scan.json --format md --output reports/report.md` for a styled report.\n\nLicense: MIT — Use only on systems you own or are authorised to test.\n",
