      "README.md": "# __ATM_TITLE__\n\n__ATM_DESC__\n\n## What this does\nFraud detection toolkit: rule engine (velocity, geo-mismatch, BIN risk), unsupervised IsolationForest scoring, feature engineering for tabular txn data, voice-authentication risk-scoring pipeline (audio MFCC features hook).\n\n## Install\n```bash\npip install -r requirements.txt\n```\n\n## Usage\n```bash\npython3 cli.py scan --target ./transactions.csv --output reports/fraud.json\n```\n\n## Requirements\nscikit-learn>=1.4\npandas>=2.2\nnumpy>=1.26\n\n\n## Output\n`reports/scan.json` — raw findings.\nRun `python3 cli.py report --input reports/scan.json --format md --output reports/report.md` for a styled report.\n\nLicense: MIT — Use only on systems you own or are authorised to test.\n",
      "cli.py": "#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"CLI entry point — fraud_detection mode.\"\"\"\nimport argparse, json, sys, asyncio\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom core.runner import Runner\nfrom core.reporter import Reporter\nfrom core.config import load_config\n\nMODE = \"fraud\"\n\ndef cmd_scan(args):\n    cfg = load_config(args.config)\n    cfg[\"target\"] = args.target\n    cfg[\"mode\"] = MODE\n    runner = Runner(cfg)\n    findings = asyncio.run(runner.run())\n    Path(args.output).parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    Path(args.output).write_text(json.dumps({\"target\": args.target, \"mode\": MODE, \"findings\": findings}, indent=2, default=str))\n    print(f\"[+] {len(findings)} finding(s) -> {args.output}\", file=sys.stderr)\n\ndef cmd_report(args):\n    data = json.loads(Path(args.input).read_text())\n    out = Reporter(data).render(args.format)\n    Path(args.output).write_text(out)\n    print(f\"[+] Report ({args.format}) -> {args.output}\", file=sys.stderr)\n\ndef main():\n    p = argparse.ArgumentParser(prog=\"fraud_detection\", description=\"fraud_detection — fraud mode\")\n    sub = p.add_subparsers(dest=\"cmd\", required=True)\n    s = sub.add_parser(\"scan\");   s.add_argument(\"--target\", required=True); s.add_argument(\"--config\", default=\"config.yaml\"); s.add_argument(\"--output\", default=\"reports/scan.json\"); s.set_defaults(fn=cmd_scan)\n    r = sub.add_parser(\"report\"); r.add_argument(\"--input\", required=True); r.add_argument(\"--format\", choices=[\"json\",\"html\",\"csv\",\"md\"], default=\"md\"); r.add_argument(\"--output\", default=\"reports/report.md\"); r.set_defaults(fn=cmd_report)\n    a = p.parse_args(); a.fn(a)\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\": main()\n",
